										      filename of the SVG to render,<code>svgfill</code>accepts a value to
										      change the default fill color of the SVG element from black,<code>svgstroke</code>accepts a value to change the svg stroke color
										      (default is none).</p><div class="flex flex-wrap mt-3"> <div class="sm:w-1/2 pr-4 pl-4"><h5>Example</h5><pre><code class="language-twig"></code></pre> {% endverbatim %} {% include '@atoms/svg/_svg--icon.twig' with {
